{"tid":1990701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"限聚令定義差　執法亂　大狀：如法律黑洞","createTime":"2020-04-27T01:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T02:27:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e540b82e83487376dde212394ab264a26d42922","tid":1990701,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】限聚令與緊急法相似，兩者均以附屬法例形式訂立，未經立法會或公眾討論。有大律師指出，限聚令最大問題是未就「聚集」一詞下清晰定義，字眼混亂，加上執法不一，莫講市民，連一班大狀亦無所適從。有大狀開玩笑，司法機構公告5月4日恢服全面運作，法院門外一定大排長龍，法例只豁免「工作地點」的聚集，「咁係咪可以拉晒我地？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/OG77SXOIMPMD5PNRORDHMW7XOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2FOG77SXOIMPMD5PNRORDHMW7XOE%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4FGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=e9214702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2FOG77SXOIMPMD5PNRORDHMW7XOE%2F&h=4465916c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/OG77SXOIMPMD5PNRORDHMW7XOE/</a>"},{"pid":"92686c594673a4d1c6a7482a8eaf6e9bcc5a5395","tid":1990701,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"5月4日如果法院門外大排長龍<br />\n有兩三個人去嗰到屌柒啲人違反限聚令同埋報狗就精彩"},{"pid":"6497fe53333dc8e86b2e67f1cb9438cfa6e69415","tid":1990701,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92686c594673a4d1c6a7482a8eaf6e9bcc5a5395","tid":1990701,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"5月4日如果法院門外大排長龍<br />\n有兩三個人去嗰到屌柒啲人違反限聚令同埋報狗就精彩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T02:27:51.000Z","msg":"旁聽師排隊會唔會比狗搞"}]}